OL,3,CJersey politicians back new school
OL,4,Cover extending town park
OL,6,FA proposal that would have delayed
OL,7,Fplans for a new primary school next to
OL,8,FSt Helier's Millennium Town Park has
OL,9,Fbeen rejected.
OL,11,FOn Tuesday, Jersey States Members
OL,12,Fvoted 31-10 against Constable Simon
OL,13,FCrowcroft's proposition, which argued
OL,14,Ffor a pause to any development while a
OL,15,Ffull review takes place, suggesting
OL,16,Fthat the derelict former Jersey Gas
OL,17,Fsite could be turned into further
OL,18,Fgreen space.
