OL,6,FHe wrote: "The case for a fully
OL,7,Fobjective and comprehensive
OL,8,Freconsideration of the future uses of
OL,9,Fthe site has only grown stronger."
OL,11,FMinisters supporting the school
OL,12,Fproject say it will combine the
OL,13,Fexisting campuses of Springfield, St
OL,14,FLuke's and La Passerelle, which are no
OL,15,Flonger deemed fit for purpose.
OL,17,FAhead of the debate, some residents
OL,18,Fmade their voices clear outside the
OL,19,FStates Chamber, urging politicians
OL,20,Fthrough a peaceful protest to create
OL,21,Fmore green space on the site instead.
