OL,3,CJersey politicians back new school
OL,4,Cover extending town park
OL,6,FBernie Manning told ITV News: "There
OL,7,Fare so many other activities that
OL,8,Fcould be introduced to the park.
OL,10,F"If we were to have another Covid
OL,11,F(pandemic) or anything like that, we
OL,12,Fneed these big open spaces in town."
OL,14,FFreya Gallichan added: "The park's
OL,15,Fgreat for the whole community,
OL,16,Fobviously children included, but a
OL,17,Fvery large school would block and take
OL,18,Fover the site - is that the best for
OL,19,Fus? We just ask them to think again."
