OL,6,FStates Members were also divided on
OL,7,Fthe issue.
OL,9,FDeputy Montford Tadier rejected
OL,10,Faccusations from campaigners that the
OL,11,FGovernment is proposing to build "a
OL,12,Fluxury new school".
OL,14,FHe added: "That is one step too far -
OL,15,Fit's just a fit for purpose, modern
OL,16,Fschool."
OL,18,FMeanwhile, Deputy Max Andrews argued
OL,19,FSt Helier's residents "deserve more
OL,20,Fgreen space".
