OL,6,FQuestions have been raised over the
OL,7,Fextent to which other locations were
OL,8,Fconsidered for the primary school.
OL,10,FHowever, Jersey's Infrastructure
OL,11,FMinister, Andy Jehan, told ITV News
OL,12,Fthat this was the best option after a
OL,13,Freview of around 40 different sites.
OL,15,FDeputy Sam Mezec told the Assembly:
OL,16,F"We should deliver this project in the
OL,17,Finterest of the children of St Helier."
