OL,6,FITV News understands that States
OL,7,FMembers have already allocated #12
OL,8,Fmillion to the school project, with
OL,9,Fwork due to begin as early as next
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FAlongside concerns about the quality
OL,13,Fof St Helier's primary schools, some
OL,14,Fministers cited Jersey's growing
OL,15,Fpopulation - which increased by 510
OL,16,Flast year and 350 in 2023.
